title: ASUS Pentium Quad Core - (4 GB/1 TB HDD/Windows 10 Home) X543MA-DM101T Laptop  (15.6 inch, Transparent Silver, 1.90 kg)

product_specification.Sales Package: Laptop, Power Adaptor, User Guide, Warranty Documents
product_specification.Clock Speed: 1.1 GHz with Turbo Boost Upto 2.7 GHz
product_specification.USB Port: 1 x USB 3.2 (1st Gen) Type A, 2 x USB 2.0 Type A
product_specification.Screen Type: HD LED Backlit Anti-glare IPS Display (200 nits Brightness, 45% NTSC Color Gamut, 75% Screen-to-body Ratio)
product_specification.Additional Features: 33 WHrs Li-ion Battery, BIOS Setup User Password, BIOS Booting User Password Protection, HDD User Password Protection and Security

product_description.Stylish and Lightweight Build: This elegant-looking laptop from ASUS weighs just about 1.9 kg, allowing you to comfortably take it along with you wherever you go. The premium finish lends it a classy and stylish look which is sure to grab the attention of onlookers.
product_description.Powerful Performance: Powered by an Intel Pentium quad-core N5000 processor and 4 GB of DDR4 RAM, this laptop helps you finish your tasks with ease and efficiency.
product_description.Large Storage Capacity: You can store all your favorite movies, videos, photos, documents, and other content on this laptop as it comes with an HDD that has a large storage space of up to 1 TB.
product_description.Multiple Connectivity Options: Offering a plethora of connectivity options, such as a USB 3.2 Type-A (Gen 1) port, two USB 2.0 Type-A ports, an HDMI output, and a microSD card reader, this laptop from ASUS makes it easy to connect a wide range of compatible devices to it. The USB 3.2 Type-A port helps you transfer files quickly via compatible USB devices and the HDMI output port lets you connect this laptop to a compatible TV or monitor.
product_description.ASUS SonicMaster and ASUS Audio Wizard: Get ready to experience every beat to its fullest as this laptop comes with ASUS SonicMaster and ASUS Audio Wizard technologies. The ASUS SonicMaster’s professional-grade codec, featuring the right combination of hardware, software, and audio tuning, ensures precise audio encoding and decoding, taking your aural experience to the next level. Moreover, the amplifiers, large speakers, and resonance chambers further make it a delight to listen to songs, play games, and watch movies on this laptop. Furthermore, the powerful software suite of the ASUS Audio Wizard ensures that it can achieve the perfect audio balance, irrespective of the content you’re listening to. You can even manually adjust the audio settings to suit your listening needs via this suite, so you can truly enjoy an immersive sound experience.
product_description.ASUS Splendid Technology: The ASUS Splendid technology of this laptop offers an enhanced visual experience, be it while playing games or watching videos. It includes four display modes, such as the Vivid mode (boosts contrast), Eye Care mode (minimizes blue-light levels, preventing eye strain), Normal mode (for daily tasks), and the Manual mode (for personalized color adjustments). The ASUS Tru2Life Video technology helps boost the sharpness and contrast of every pixel in a video frame by almost 150%, so you can enjoy optimized image quality, every single time.
product_description.Clear and Loud Audio: This ASUS laptop comes with dual 2 W stereo speakers that are enclosed within a large 19.4cc chamber, so you can enjoy an immersive and stunning aural experience with enhanced bass. Also, these speakers make use of every cubic millimeter of the chassis space, thereby delivering clear and low-frequency sound clarity.
product_description.Keyboard: Whether it’s to play games or type a large assignment, the full-size, one-piece chiclet keyboard of this laptop makes typing on it a seamless and comfortable experience. It offers a key travel of about 1.8 mm and minimal key float, making it a delight to type and play.
product_description.ASUS IceCool Technology: This laptop uses the ASUS IceCool technology to address the heating issues of the laptop. This technology ensures that the heat build-up under the palm rest is prevented by maintaining the temperature of that area within the range of 28°C to 35°C. Also, the internal layout is designed in such a way that the heat-producing components are placed away from you.

review:
I just bought this laptop after exchanging my 10 year old lenovo core i3 in 8300 Rs.
The laptop is great though the build quality is not top notch and you can feel it immediately. But very light weight and shows premium looks.
I have opened numerous multitasking on first day, did some office work and some light poker on adda52 and baazi apps. All worked without a issue.
All in all a good laptop for day to day work and light gaming.
One more things, the keys are soft and feel delicate so dont hit it like keybord or else I feel it can be damaged in no time.
